need_lock = read_seqretry(seq);<br />  rcu_read_unlock();<br /><br />  if (need_lock) {<br />    get_real_lock();<br /><br />    .. do lookup ..<br /><br />    drop_real_lock();<br /> }<br /><br />which just falls back to a locked access if the rcu model doesn't work.<br /><br />                             Linus<br /><br /><br /></pre><div align="center"><div class="shariff" data-services="[&quot;reddit&quot;]" data-theme="grey" data-lang="en" data-backend-url="//shariff.lkml.org/index.php"></div></div></td><td width="32" rowspan="2" class="c" valign="top"><img src="/images/icornerr.gif" width="32" height="32" alt="\" /></td></tr><tr><td align="right" valign="bottom">
